message.content:
Here is a CSV file that contains information about the first five presidents of the United States.

```
Name,Age When Started Office,Year Started Office,Number of Years Served
George Washington,57,1789,8
John Adams,63,1797,1
Thomas Jefferson,57,1801,2
James Madison,62,1809,2
James Monroe,63,1817,2
```

This CSV includes their names, the age they were when they started in office, the year they began their tenure, and the number of years they served. Please note that the ages are at the start of their presidency and have been rounded to the nearest whole number. Also, the "Number of Years Served" is an approximation as the exact number of years can vary based on the day of the month they started and ended their terms.
